text: Phira musa nu usa di kauma vicom kujha naujavanam tom binham kise ne na mani'a. Phirana de dara ate khuda apani kauma de vade saradaram de dara tom ki kite uha unham nu ko'i musakala vica na pa dena. Isa la'i ki phira'auna dharati upara takata rakhada si ate uha unham lokam vicom si jihare hadam nu tapa jande sana
